  			<div id="item-2845"><p>Rebecca, I have no suggestions since I have not been to Spain yet.  But it sure sounds like a great way to celebrate your marriage journey thus far.  Have a great time!</p></div>
  			<div class="date byline">
  				
  				<span><span class="alias">Gerda</span></span>
  				<span>on September 29, 2006</span>
  			</div>
  		</div><div>
  			<div id="item-2846"><p>My best meals in Barcelona were had at a selection of restaurants within the Grupo Tragaluz. Check out the web site for more info: http://www.grupotragaluz.com/</p>
<p>The one that sticks out the most for me was Bestial. Excellent fusion-y cuisine. Contemporary architecture seems to be a theme with a lot of the restaurants within  Grupo. They were definitely hot spots for dining. The Hotel Omm is fantastic.</p></div>
